description:
Translates Young Avengers #5.

Who ARE the Young Avengers? Discover their deepest secrets in this issue! In the penultimate chapter of "Sidekicks," the Young Avengers are finally forced to reveal the true nature of their powers as their battle with Kang the Conqueror becomes a fight to the death -- and that's not hyperbole! But will the team survive its first fatality? (Spanish Version)

description:
Goon and Franky stumble upon a bizarre freak show at Brigadoon's Dreamland Carnival, where the evil barker pits the Goon against a horrendous, bacon-eating behemoth, the Ten-in-One!

GooncreatorEric Powell teams with acclaimed writerEvan Dorkin(Beasts of Burden)!

After being sent to the Age of Apocalypse dimension by Dark Beast, Wolverine and his team fight for possession of a Life Seed, an object that is able to save Warren from becoming the new Apocalypse. But upon arriving back home, the team finds a free Archangel and his four horsemen waiting. After an intense battle the team is left in shambles. Part of the team tries to regroup while Psylocke tries to reach Warren in an entirely different way and before he does something he will forever regret.
